description.en: GoCrypto is set to change the way people discover, purchase, track and resell items online. With its unique features, it will offer users a “one-place”, from where they can shop in all the online stores anywhere in the world, check the value of items in their inventory and learn the best time to sell those items. GoCrypto will offer users a completely decentralized universal loyalty program and help transform every household into a business while are also bringing cryptocurrencies mainstream by offering crypto payments for online stores that don't offer them yet. GoCrypto was previously known as Eligma. It was migrated from the Ethereum to the Bitcoin Cash platform on 25 November 2019, 23:00 CET.
